title: Pixel mini motocross
description:
Jumping on a mini motocross motorcycle in an office setting


Biking in retro style pixel graphics, exciting music. 

Jumping on a motorcycle in the office. Great game to relax from work and relax.

- Funny accidents ;)

- Small size of the game only 14 mb

- Retro style

- Pixel Art

- No purchases within the app

- 8-bit music

- You can play for children
